description:
Gundam Barbatos Lupus is the mobile suit that http://anidb.net/ch76361 [Mikazuki Augus] pilots. After many battles, and upgrades from Teiwaz, it has taken on a new form with enhanced weaponry. The mobile suit is one of the Gundam Frames used in the Calamity War 300 years ago.
Source: ANN
name: ASW-G-08 Gundam Barbatos Lupus
